Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau ke perpustakaan\Nsama Tani pas liburan kemarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho lihat kalian, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan? Kencan di perpustakaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Polos banget, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}habis itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ceritaku enggak penting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kabarnya, Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu lo, cewek yang tukaran kontak\Ndenganmu sebelum liburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami lumayan sering kontak-kontakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi cuma itu doang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:00:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak lancar, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun kami kirim pesan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kebanyakan mikir,\Njadi bingung mau balas apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat banget balasnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi balasan Yamada kaku banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Pesanku kepanjangan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan aku dianggap menyeramkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau enggak suka, abaikan saja dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan enggak suka, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia tanya\Napa aku mau ngobrol lewat telepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah dua kali kutolak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya dia tahu aku refleks bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak bermaksud nolak dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kesannya kayak nolak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas agak canggung, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau dia balas pesan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin dia memang enggak pandai bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak ngerti lagi, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku penasaran dia orangnya bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira seleramu cewek ceria\Nyang murah senyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menarik juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang benar, sih…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya ringkasan singkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lucu banget, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, cowok yang lemah\Nterhadap senyuman tak terduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu suatu hari…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mungkin sudah sadar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku suka padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kita pacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada mungkin enggak kelihatan begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia pacaran cukup lama sama mantannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami masih berteman baik, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini masa muda yang kuinginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu, kau masih punya waktu\Nbuat menikmati masa muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku iri sama orang\Nyang punya hubungan yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya aku bisa belajar banyak hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah punya pacar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pacar pertamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku masih meraba-raba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bersikap\Nseolah Ri enggak pernah ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memetik sesuatu yang hijau
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya enggak masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di seragam sekolah kita…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau beli pelindung lencana\Nsama boneka pajangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon, lihat orang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Tani, yang kuceritakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cowok berkacamata yang pacarnya gyaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kayak tokoh utama novel ringan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan tuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tani. Buruan bayar\Nterus kita cabut.
