Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toserba memang lengkap banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Siapa Ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lupakan dia, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu. Itu lo…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan cuma rasa bersalah,\Napa aku kekanak-kanakan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-teman, lihat ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menu raksasanya sudah jadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Keren banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persis kayak restoran itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tulisan tangan Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bahkan bikin ilustrasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, pro banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, Ri itu orangnya bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cowok yang baik banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya dia bakal datang ke festival.\NKayaknya kita bisa ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mau ke mana lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba barang baru di depan stasiun, yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga. Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki pacar pertamamu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau enggak pernah cemas\Nsoal apa yang harus dilakukan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau karena minim pengalaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kayaknya bukan tipe orang\Nyang peduli soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu aku meremehkan Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membandingkan diri sama dia.\NTapi sekarang aku malah ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Payah banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kepikiran terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu kurang percaya diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selesai!\N- Beres!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival budaya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dimulai sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo nikmati hari pertama ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Yuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari kedua
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dibuka untuk umum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku bakal keliling festival\Nbareng Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersenang-senanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, kausmu sudah hitam, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau juga tulis sesuatu, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tulis apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesan buat aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Untuk Suzuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan dibaca keras-keras!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dilihat juga, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau masih panggil "Suzuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Suzuki" saja enggak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya "benar" apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mulai dari mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahun lalu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya kelas kami bikin drama,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}waktu itu kami enggak sempat main.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pikirkan rencana terbaik\Nbuat mengajakmu keliling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita lihat jadwal acaranya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita lelah, ayo ke POMG
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buat minum teh dan makan kukis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lupa pameran kelas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan pameran klub seni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bosan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang cuma melihat sekilas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa auraku negatif banget, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Ada pameran di sini juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauh lebih canggung\Nsama orang yang dikenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kayak,\N"Kalian berdua anggota komite pustaka, ya?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami enggak cukup akrab\Nbuat mulai obrolan dari situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, boleh kami bicara\Nsambil lihat-lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka benaran pacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan klub fotografi kumpul?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ngomong sama aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami enggak kumpul kayak klub lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kegiatannya dilakukan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka foto ini. Warnanya cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang memotretnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, biasa saja, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka banget yang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai teknik atau kamera khusus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, enggak sehebat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma kamera pemula…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana yang kau suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fotonya memang bagus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau aslinya suka kucing, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah memberitahuku soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya bicaraku cukup lancar kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada jeda dan hening yang canggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga selalu begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan gugup.\NLebih lugas dan langsung ke intinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau di mana?\NBiar kujemput.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersikaplah lebih ceria dan ramah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi lihat apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih energik…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama enggak ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, mau keluar dan lihat-lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, aku enggak tahu\Nsiapa yang datang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kau berubah juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakal kalah kalau begitu terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, dunia luar mungkin menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada ada di kelas ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Tadi dia di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba teleponnya ditutup.\NKe mana dia pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kucari sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ganteng banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Barusan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seru banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang banget dapat hadiah\Ndari stan Lempar Sasaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahaya kalau enggak lihat depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Suzuki…\N- Miyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga itu kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama enggak ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rihito…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sato, lama enggak ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau di sini.\N- Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kenal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman sekelas pas SMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia teman sekelasku pas SMP, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sendirian di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, sama teman SMA-ku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pisah sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar-dengar Yamada, Sato,\Ndan Miyu sekelas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, aku ingin ketemu kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, lama banget, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa lama, tuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak lihat kalian sejak lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kabar kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik-baik saja, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Canggung banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah lama banget,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami cuma bisa basa-basi sambil senyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Yamada! Buruan sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira setelah selama ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa pura-pura enggak ada apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata aku salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Andai kita enggak bikin canggung…\N- Lelucon irama memang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang aneh darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tak bisa lari dari keajaiban irama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan kau jadi ahli?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua pacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu bareng terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Repot banget, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa enggak jadian saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kalian kelihatan serasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di situasi begini, makin canggung\Nkalau kami terus menyangkal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pura-pura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bikin Miyu nolak aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu, mau pacaran sama aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lo?\N- Selamat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, dianggap serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berpikir "mungkin enggak buruk juga",\Nkami mulai pacaran…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Canggung banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Napa yang kita obrolin sebelumnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu kami selalu ketawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi setelah pacaran,\Nmalah sama sekali enggak asyik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lakukan hal-hal kayak orang pacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak benci, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah aku suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susah dijelaskan,\Ntapi rasanya enggak benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatan aneh, 'kan?\NHubungan kita bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan saja. Kita balik kayak dulu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berteman saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memaksa dia mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bikin dia baca situasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin dipikir aku salah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin mengganggu pikiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta maaf rasanya egois banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya cuma ingin\Nmenenangkan hati nurani sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reuni SMP kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak akan datang\Nkalau aku datang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agak merepotkan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatirkan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kumpul kayak biasa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo baikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah! Aku mau cari Dayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rihito…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bikin dia baca situasi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Kalian belum baikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bilangnya, ya?\NKurasa kami baru saja baikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya semua kecanggungan lama\Nhilang dalam sekejap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian anak SMP sepertinya mengerti,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalian kacangin kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, 'kan, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tinggal kalian berdua, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, kami sempat pacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi rasanya langsung enggak sreg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sengaja disembunyikan,\Nrasanya seperti berbuat jahat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kuceritakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cari mati sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma kesalahan kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau sekarang atau dulu, kami cuma teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang masuk akal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani enggak suka cewek\Nyang punya "masa lalu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa kau pacar pertamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf bikin kau menghiburku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya ini masalahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau cari angin dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi gara-gara itu, Miyu dan aku baikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian lagi berantem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu. Paham maksudku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paham banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti merelakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan ingat kesalahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, lebih dari jatuh cinta,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak mau dibenci teman-temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada yang bakal membencimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksud "ini masalahku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cemburu doang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sama Rihito\Nenggak ada hubungan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian Ri lumayan ganteng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seganteng apa pun dia\Natau sedekat apa pun kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau biarpun dia cowok,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan berarti\Naku bisa jatuh cinta sama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang kupelajari saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan enggak ada apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya penyesalan dan hal-hal\Nyang sudah kurenungkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pacar pertama bagi kalian berdua?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, tuh. Terdengar murni banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejarah cintaku sudah berantakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak masalah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalah enggak punya masa lalu,\Natau kali pertama, semua itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh kalau mikir "murni" itu artinya\Nenggak ada apa-apa di masa lalu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Kau berubah pikiran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biarpun aku cewek yang sudah\Npeluk 100 cowok di masa lalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selama aku ingin hadapi orang\Ndi depanku dengan tulus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu dianggap cinta murni, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke! Aku mau temui Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba aku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingin banget jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan? Taira, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia punya hubungan yang aku enggak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menduga sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percuma mikirin masa lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kumpul kayak biasa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku peduli sama hal-hal kecil,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekarang dan di masa depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku enggak makin pede tiap harinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malah jadi serakah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan makin berpikiran sempit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka sifatmu yang enggak bisa bohong,\Ndan kau selalu paham perasaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kadang-kadang…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahkan saat hatimu kacau,\Nkau pura-pura enggak peduli, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun enggak jelas\Natau masih kau pikirkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau ada yang mengganggumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bilang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Upacara penghargaan akan segera dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua murid, harap berkumpul di gimnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita di sini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu percuma\Nmembandingkan diri sama orang lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku terus gelisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu aku mulai benci diriku\Nkarena merasa begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Bukan aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf bikin kau gelisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya dia cocok denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada banyak orang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang lebih cocok buatmu daripada aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana kutahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obrolan macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Miyu".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang panggil kau begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma Rihito yang suka beda sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rihito…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kalau ada yang mau diomongin,\Nbilang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas 2-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tani Yusuke.\N- Kalau begitu, Yu…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harap segera datang ke gimnasium!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Yusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada orang di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka panggil nama kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pasti bakal diledek nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, 'kan, Yusuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak perlu memaksa diri\Nmemanggilku begitu.
